T07TD4086E:37b-3: rtse zhing dga' la dga' dgur spyod de /
T07TD4086E:37b-4: rang gi las kyi 'bras bu nyams su myong ngo //

T07TD4086E:37b-6: me tog phreng bar bkod pa bzhin du gyur pa ni /
T07TD4086E:37b-7: dper na me tog phreng rgyud dam ;
T07TD4086E:37b-8: me tog phreng rgyud kyi slob ma mkhas pas me tog gi phreng ba tha gu la brgyus pa dang /
T07TD4086E:37b-9: me tog gi rna rgyan legs par byas pa bzhin te /
T07TD4086E:37b-10: thang las skyes pa'i bya sna tshogs skad snyan cing 'jebs pa dang /
T07TD4086E:37b-13: 'dod dgur sgyur ba'i gzugs can rnams skad snyan pa 'byin to //

T07TD4086E:37b-25: dkar po rnam pa bzhi yod do //

T07TD4086E:37b-32: rgyan sna tshogs lag rgyan dang /

T07TD4086E:38a-19: / de dag thams cad kyang gzugs bzang zhing blta na sdug la mdzes pa me tog ku mu ta'i mdog ltar thal kar du 'dug cing yan lag bdun shin tu legs par gnas te /
